{
  "text": "Learning representations using both textual and visual information has also been explored using deep architectures. These representations show promising results for learning a mapping between visual data [CITATION_1] the same way that it was shown for text [CITATION_2] . We differ from these methods as our objective is to directly optimized for analogy questions and our method does not use textual information.",
